{"bill":{"bill_id":1650386,"change_hash":"82968a5e2bcfea4df78d939695b74bdc","session_id":1988,"session":{"session_id":1988,"state_id":46,"year_start":2023,"year_end":2023,"prefile":0,"sine_die":0,"prior":0,"special":0,"session_tag":"Regular Session","session_title":"2023 Regular Session","session_name":"2023 Regular Session"},"url":"https:\/\/legiscan.com\/VA\/bill\/SB1069\/2023","state_link":"https:\/\/lis.virginia.gov\/cgi-bin\/legp604.exe?231+sum+SB1069","completed":0,"status":3,"status_date":"2023-02-24","progress":[{"date":"2023-01-09","event":1},{"date":"2023-01-09","event":9},{"date":"2023-01-19","event":10},{"date":"2023-02-02","event":10},{"date":"2023-02-06","event":2},{"date":"2023-02-10","event":9},{"date":"2023-02-16","event":10},{"date":"2023-02-24","event":3}],"state":"VA","state_id":46,"bill_number":"SB1069","bill_type":"B","bill_type_id":"1","body":"S","body_id":8,"current_body":"S","current_body_id":8,"title":"Pedestrians; drivers stopping at certain signs.","description":"Drivers stopping for pedestrians; certain signs; stops. Requires the driver of a vehicle on a highway approaching a pedestrian who is crossing such highway to stop when such pedestrian is within the driver's lane or within an adjacent lane and approaching the driver's lane. Currently, a driver is required to yield the right-of-way to such pedestrian by stopping and remaining stopped. The bill also provides that localities that are already authorized to install signs directing motor vehicles to yield the right-of-way to pedestrians crossing or attempting to cross a highway may also install signs directing motor vehicles to stop for such pedestrians. Drivers stopping for pedestrians; certain signs; stops. Requires the driver of a vehicle on a highway approaching a pedestrian who is crossing such highway to stop when such pedestrian is within the driver's lane or within an adjacent lane and approaching the driver's lane. Currently, a driver is required to yield the right-of-way to s